    nrMirrorSyncPriority   OBJECT-TYPE
        SYNTAX  INTEGER
        ACCESS  read-only
        STATUS  mandatory
        DESCRIPTION
            "The mirror synchronization priority when a NAS resource enable
the mirror property."
